{"tid":1910481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"WHO警告：各國應增產口罩！","createTime":"2020-03-04T16:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T08:36:14.000Z","uid":226548,"like":3,"dislike":235,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"42debc1c1af09c9940d8a21a21dfd8a07641597e","tid":1910481,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gbS80Nm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgbS80Nm.png&h=439d3b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>WHO呼籲全球廠商提高手套、口罩產量</strong><br />\n<br />\n「我們不能像應對流感一樣應對新冠肺炎疫情！」<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">譚德塞表示，目前最令人擔心的是醫療耗材的短缺。</span></strong>手術口罩的價格已經上漲了6倍，N95呼吸器上漲了3倍，手術衣的價格翻倍。<br />\n<br />\nWHO估計，應對新冠肺炎，全球每個月需要8900萬醫用口罩、7600萬檢測手套和160萬護目鏡。WHO已經發布了指南，指導在醫療場所如何合理使用PPE，和有效管理供應鏈。<br />\n<br />\n在全球範圍內，估計個人防護裝備（PPE）的供應需要提高40%；WHO呼籲製造商緊急提高生產，滿足需求並確保貨源。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">譚德塞也呼籲各國政府，推出措施激勵製造商提高產能</span></strong>。，這包括放寬對PPE和其它醫療供給的出口限制。<br />\n<br />\n文/林以璿 圖/何宜庭"},{"pid":"22293d4414d037f66c67b7d400cc45881be0b6c7","tid":1910481,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:53:45.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/home/who警告-新冠肺炎跟流感有4點不-樣-呼籲各國增產口罩-090030850.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2Fwho%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E8%B7%9F%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E6%9C%894%E9%BB%9E%E4%B8%8D-%E6%A8%A3-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E5%A2%9E%E7%94%A2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-090030850.html&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=f2186ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/home/who警告-新冠肺炎跟流感有4點不-樣-呼籲各國增產口罩-090030850.html</a>"},{"pid":"a7283abb370c21930a0be4266f4c72c65ba586c1","tid":1910481,"uid":179729,"like":178,"dislike":1,"score":177,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"洗撚你講咩，on99"},{"pid":"f57bf63d61cbcad46057e0a0fb259766811268